item.title: CVE-2022-48330|2024-08-03T15:10:59.699Z -- huawei -- flmg-10
item.description: A Huawei sound box product has an out-of-bounds write vulnerability. Attackers can exploit this vulnerability to cause buffer overflow. Affected product versions include:FLMG-10 versions FLMG-10 10.0.1.0(H100SP22C00).
